Reviews: On August 2018, Juan and his team fed 100 hungry people on my daughter's birthday party. I was able to choose four (4) different meats (Asada, Chorizo con Papa, Pastor & Chicken) plus the Salsas, Aguas Frescas, rice, beans, etc....All were delicious! I was delighted with their service, food quality, taste, and professionalism. I will hire Taquisas Los Juanes for future needs for sure! Recommended 100%

We hired Los Juanes for my daughter's birthday and everyone loved their tacos. Every meat was delicious!  The aguas frescas were delicious! The beans. The rice.  Everything was great!  The service was awesome, and they're reasonably priced!  Everyone at the party loved the tacos they even got up for 2nds! I highly recommend them!

Replies: * Delicious meat dishes * Delicious aguas frescas * Great beans and rice

Reviews: I hired Los Juanes for a birthday party a few weeks back and the food was delicious! The staff is very professional yet fun at the same time. They are also very clean which is a huge deal for me. I was a little nervous to hire them because they had just started up not too long ago but I have no regrets. I loved how they had a variety of different items that they offer, not just tacos. I will definitely hire them again!
Relevant Content: *the food was delicious *they had a variety of different items that they offer, not just tacos.
Replies: * Delicious food * Wide variety of items, not just tacos

Reviews: Hired Juan last weekend for a birthday party. He was professional and prices are reasonable. Best of all food was delicious. 2 of our guests already asked for his contact info.

Summary: It seems like the reviews for Taquisas Los Juanes are overwhelmingly positive when it comes to the food quality. Many customers raved about the tacos and seafood dishes, like the aguachile, stating that they were amazing. Reviews consistently mentioned that the food had great flavor and that all the items on the menu were delicious. The meat dishes and aguas frescas were also praised, as well as the beans and rice. It's worth noting that many reviews simply stated that the food was delicious without specifying a particular item. Overall, the food quality at Taquisas Los Juanes seems to be excellent.
